title: Bigfoot Series 11.25 in. Kid's Poly Snow Shovel with Steel Core Handle
description: The Bigfoot kid's snow shovel is the perfect shovel for your child to help clear snow off driveways, yards or decks. While shovelling snow might seem like a chore, shovelling snow alongside your child can be a fun bonding experience. The Bigfoot kid's snow shovel is made with a plastic head and d-grip, so that it is both lightweight and child safe. The shovel is also bright orange so that it can be easily seen in the snow if misplaced.
